<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and Base Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #eef5f9;
            color: #333;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2193b0, #6dd5ed);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6dd5ed, #2193b0);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 50px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .contact h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2193b0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .contact p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .contact-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            outline: none;
            transition: border 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus {
            border-color: #2193b0;
        }
        .contact-form button {
            padding: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #43cea2, #185a9d);
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-form button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .contact-form button:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #43cea2, #185a9d);
            color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #6dd5ed;
        }

        /* Media Queries */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                padding: 15px 10px;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            .contact h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Get in Touch</div>
        <div>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>We’d Love to Hear From You!</h1>
        <p>Got questions, feedback, or partnership ideas? Let's connect and make things happen!</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Our Team</h2>
        <p>Our team is here to assist you. Fill out the form below, and we’ll respond promptly.</p>
        <form class="contact-form" action="/submit-contact" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>
            <textarea name="message" placeholder="How can we help you?" rows="5" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Contact Us. Your feedback drives us forward. <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
